Andriy Kushnerov - a unique fighter and innovator. A Belarusian politician who joined the Armed Forces of Ukraine after February 24th to defend Ukraine.
Do not miss this impressive meeting!

Right to Protection Poland invites participants aged 10 to 13 years to a free webinar where they will find interesting games and exercises for developing self-esteem and self-understanding.

Meeting goals:
formation and development of constructive communication skills and abilities
familiarize participants with the basic techniques of information exchange, develop the ability to process it, find vital aspects in the received information to solve current problems;
develop respect for others and oneself among participants, teach how to overcome inner unrest, support each other, trust and be trustworthy;

to learn to achieve success without rivalry, to believe that all this is necessary even at school.

   Speaker: Olena Lyashenko, psychologist R2P Poland.

When: Thursday, December 12, 18:00‚Äì19:30

Registration at the link:

üìç Online

P.S: with care for you, dear ones ü•∞

text_entities.TRANSLATED_TEXT: Happy Victorious New Year
Dear ones!!!!

I wish in the New Year to find something valuable for yourself, keep what's important, acquire the best, preserve the dearest, lose the bad, forgive the insults, forget the sad. HAPPINESS IN THE NEW YEAR!!! May everything we planned come true, everything we wanted to start - begin, and what we wanted to finish - end. The best New Year's gifts you will never find under the Christmas tree! These are children, family, relatives, friends. May they always be with you!!! Cherish what is most precious to you! Health, prosperity, and joy in the New Year!!! Best New Year's hugs for you from me! With respect, Anna!
